{"tid":182220,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(新手上路) Vw DSG波箱控制/保養","createTime":"2017-04-01T07:13:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T12:19:58.000Z","uid":101942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"51d0db3b662e26d6e8afccb580a1a84145872ce6","tid":182220,"uid":101942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:13:32.000Z","msg":"買左架二手golf gt<br />\n第一次用DSG 唔太熟<br />\n頭幾次揸個時<br />\n一比油 一波上二波<br />\n有少少震 <br />\n上到二波 就順番 唔會有震<br />\n揸左一排 熟左少少<br />\n比油就會細力少少 順住上<br />\n就少左震既情況好多<br />\n想問下大家起步會點架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新手post 有咩錯唔好怪"},{"pid":"313cbcd890eba4bb8852398b61f014e33371dee4","tid":182220,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"上到2波先踩深啲，因為一波太短"},{"pid":"7f9411ba41482560187449487de5c35b64221dcb","tid":182220,"uid":7644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:31:00.000Z","msg":"二波因為個clutch未放哂，深油就會震<br />\n<br />\n等個轉數上番啲再踩就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec73dfa42e7ee574e611c4543facd6306a9c6b7a","tid":182220,"uid":7644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T08:32:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二波因為個clutch未放哂，深油就會震<br />\n<br />\n等個轉數上番啲再踩就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起得快就一開波就踩深啲，令到佢一波轉數上高啲先轉二波"},{"pid":"6250883d4179d0a5479b39f77d910872fbd04377","tid":182220,"uid":52323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T09:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>二波因為個clutch未放哂，深油就會震<br />\n<br />\n等個轉數上番啲再踩就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起得快就一開波就踩深啲，令到佢一波轉數上高啲先轉二波</blockquote><br />\n用s波輕鬆解決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23cbbe416218aa3d9ea159fe330be6c167a3120","tid":182220,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T10:58:10.000Z","msg":"揸得 DSG 就踩快D<br />\n唔好妹下妹下搞到半離合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fd3fe69a98e3b9f1e619534ec8afb4baff9eee4","tid":182220,"uid":101942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>二波因為個clutch未放哂，深油就會震<br />\n<br />\n等個轉數上番啲再踩就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起得快就一開波就踩深啲，令到佢一波轉數上高啲先轉二波</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數一開就踩深會大機會震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而慢慢踩 <br />\n去到8-12公里轉二波就無震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6723fbf09a88e7b5a111d2870245c24c74b24683","tid":182220,"uid":101942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>揸得 DSG 就踩快D<br />\n唔好妹下妹下搞到半離合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一起步就踩？"},{"pid":"d898ea90b6f48690225ab709687e048bf0db5c67","tid":182220,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T13:33:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>揸得 DSG 就踩快D<br />\n唔好妹下妹下搞到半離合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一起步就踩？</blockquote><br />\nDSG 起步要 Clutch in 會有 delay<br />\n等架車一郁就可以踩快小小上 D3<br />\n如果用 Auto hold 就踩輕半秒再踩深"},{"pid":"7da7e8feca72f2c2cad05110bc710902e34f0b60","tid":182220,"uid":6343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T21:34:02.000Z","msg":"震一震果下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好掛住個DSG波箱<br />\n<br />\n利申mk6"},{"pid":"fdab1466d8f8d8221f83af08cf32eccae07543c4","tid":182220,"uid":101201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:00:21.000Z","msg":"唔好搞咁多野   dsg遲早都會死<br />\n<br />\n利申：過年前先換左一次波箱電腦"},{"pid":"13df5feef9f008bdd2d35696a89036664a593ed1","tid":182220,"uid":67527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:41:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好搞咁多野   dsg遲早都會死<br />\n<br />\n利申：過年前先換左一次波箱電腦</blockquote><br />\n新車最後返幾年廠，佢啲software都幾多bug，唔返去update新電腦software容易啲死。"},{"pid":"46f78a32a2012163264eb696cd45e5dac69fb4b2","tid":182220,"uid":101942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:25:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好搞咁多野   dsg遲早都會死<br />\n<br />\n利申：過年前先換左一次波箱電腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打可以講下做咩死左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd86511fec63005ce6998cabd0633a5eded7ee1","tid":182220,"uid":31809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔好搞咁多野   dsg遲早都會死<br />\n<br />\n利申：過年前先換左一次波箱電腦</blockquote><br />\nDQ200 真係唔可以 chip<br />\n因為本身 stock 已經到左 design limit <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8630b8f626f8c49a45c42c6ff73fca1b725893","tid":182220,"uid":101201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T15:36:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔好搞咁多野   dsg遲早都會死<br />\n<br />\n利申：過年前先換左一次波箱電腦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n爸打可以講下做咩死左？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行行下無lala出左個士巴拿個圖案   死呢d通常無原因  12年車  行三萬七"},{"pid":"78e2d39102a6f8fda18d8bffe94f23e75152885e","tid":182220,"uid":45934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"好彩我架11年GT 過10萬咪都未有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591d170fb556e80ee73f78300